{"id":40,"date":"2020-09-21T04:12:15","date_gmt":"2020-09-21T04:12:15","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/localhost\/?p=40"},"modified":"2020-09-21T14:31:41","modified_gmt":"2020-09-21T14:31:41","slug":"iot-esp8266-01","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"http:\/\/localhost\/2020\/09\/21\/iot-esp8266-01\/","title":{"rendered":"IOT-ESP8266: 01-T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u module esp8266 v\u00e0 kh\u1edfi t\u1ea1o c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Kit ESP8266 l\u00e0 kit ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n Wifi SoC v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00ec t\u00edch h\u1ee3p s\u1eb5n m\u1ea1ch n\u1ea1p s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ic CP2102 tr\u00ean borad. B\u00ean trong ESP8266 c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n m\u1ed9t l\u00f5i vi x\u1eed l\u00fd v\u00ec th\u1ebf b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp l\u1eadp tr\u00ecnh cho ESP8266 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n th\u00eam b\u1ea5t k\u00ec con vi x\u1eed l\u00fd n\u00e0o n\u1eefa. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u00f3 hai ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eadp tr\u00ecnh cho ESP8266, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m IDE c\u1ee7a Arduino \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eadp tr\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n ri\u00eang ho\u1eb7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m NodeMCU<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u1edbi k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1ecf g\u1ecdn, linh ho\u1ea1t n\u00ean board d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u1edbi c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb ngo\u1ea1i vi \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh project, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m m\u1eabu m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh ch\u00f3ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td>Chip \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n<\/td><td>ESP8266EX<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>WiFi<\/td><td>2.4 GHz h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 chu\u1ea9n 802.11 b\/g\/n<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>\u0110i\u1ec7n \u00e1p ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/td><td>3.3 V<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>\u0110i\u1ec7n \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o<\/td><td>5V (th\u00f4ng qua c\u1ed5ng USB)<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>S\u1ed1 ch\u00e2n I\/O<\/td><td>11 (t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n I\/O \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 Interrupt\/PWM\/I2C\/One-wire, tr\u1eeb ch\u00e2n D0)<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>S\u1ed1 ch\u00e2n Analog Input<\/td><td>1 (\u0111i\u1ec7n \u00e1p v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i \u0111a 3.3V)<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>B\u1ed9 nh\u1edb Flash<\/td><td>4MB<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 b\u1ea3o m\u1eadt<\/td><td>WPA\/WPA2<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>T\u00edch h\u1ee3p giao th\u1ee9c<\/td><td>TCP\/IP<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>L\u1eadp tr\u00ecnh tr\u00ean c\u00e1c ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef<\/td><td>C\/C++, Micropython, NodeMCU &#8211; Lua<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>S\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 ch\u00e2n<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"666\" height=\"364\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/ESP-12E-Development-Board-ESP8266-NodeMCU-Pinout.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-133\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/ESP-12E-Development-Board-ESP8266-NodeMCU-Pinout.jpg 666w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/ESP-12E-Development-Board-ESP8266-NodeMCU-Pinout-300x164.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 666px) 100vw, 666px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>C\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>T\u1ea3i v\u00e0 c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t Arduino, tr\u00ecnh bi\u00ean d\u1ecbch v\u00e0 n\u1ea1p code cho nodemcu<\/li><li>C\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t g\u00f3i esp8266 cho Arduino<br>M\u1edf Arduino l\u00ean v\u00e0 v\u00e0o File -&gt; Preferences v\u00e0 d\u00e1n chu\u1ed7i n\u00e0y v\u00e0o: <a href=\"http:\/\/arduino.esp8266.com\/stable\/package_esp8266com_index.json\">http:\/\/arduino.esp8266.com\/stable\/package_esp8266com_index.json<\/a> -&gt; Nh\u1ea5n OK<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"723\" height=\"606\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/2019-04-28-17_18_59-.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-135\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/2019-04-28-17_18_59-.png 723w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/2019-04-28-17_18_59--300x251.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 723px) 100vw, 723px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Sau \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0o <em>Tools -&gt; Board (\u2026) -&gt; Boards Manage<\/em>r v\u00e0 g\u00f5 esp8266 v\u00e0 nh\u1ea5n Install \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e0i g\u00f3i<br><\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"608\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/1_vUaLD5aSm2iGZ_12tBrXow-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-139\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/1_vUaLD5aSm2iGZ_12tBrXow-1.png 700w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/1_vUaLD5aSm2iGZ_12tBrXow-1-300x261.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00e0o <em>Tools -&gt; Board (\u2026)&nbsp;<\/em>v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn <em>\u201cNodeMCU 1.0 (ESP 12-E module)\u201d<\/em> \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang board \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eadp tr\u00ecnh<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 setup xong g\u00f3i esp8266 tr\u00ean arduino, b\u00e0i sau ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u vi\u1ebft 1 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n \ud83d\ude00<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Kit ESP8266 l\u00e0 kit ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n Wifi SoC v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00ec t\u00edch h\u1ee3p s\u1eb5n m\u1ea1ch n\u1ea1p s\u1eed [&hellip;] <span class=\"read-more-link\"><a class=\"read-more\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost\/2020\/09\/21\/iot-esp8266-01\/\">Xem th\u00eam<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":130,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","